Affine TransformationLets go to liner algebra. While searching in the field of ECC ,you shall be aware of this transformation. This a special case in Projective transformation. Mathematics$$\vec{q} &#x3D; A\vec{p}+\vec{b}$$ In this function,A should be a Linear transformation matrix,and b is the vector for translate. we apply this function to get the Transformation. Such you have already know the basic thought of Liner Algebra,we get at$$ egin{bmatrix}q\1\end{bmatrix} &#x3D;  egin{bmatrix}A&amp;&amp;\vec{b}\0 &amp;&amp; 1 \end{bmatrix} egin{bmatrix} \vec{p}\1\end{bmatrix}$$The matrix version could be easily extended in the different dimension. Graphics ProcessingUsage.Exp: In Graphics processing ,all element vectors are just in a Euclid Plane.$$ egin{bmatrix}\vec{q}\1\end{bmatrix} &#x3D;  egin{bmatrix}A&amp;&amp;\vec{b}\0 &amp;&amp; 1 \end{bmatrix} egin{bmatrix} \vec{p}\1\end{bmatrix}$$let$$\vec{p}&#x3D;  egin{pmatrix}x_0\y_0\end{pmatrix},\vec{q}&#x3D;  egin{pmatrix}x_1\y_1\end{pmatrix},$$so$$ egin{bmatrix}x_1\y_1\1\end{bmatrix} &#x3D;  egin{bmatrix}a&amp;&amp;b&amp;&amp;c\d &amp;&amp; e&amp;&amp;f\0&amp;&amp;0&amp;&amp;1 \end{bmatrix} egin{bmatrix} x_0\y_0\1\end{bmatrix}$$Here we go.$$Let~T&#x3D; egin{bmatrix}a&amp;&amp;b&amp;&amp;c\d &amp;&amp; e&amp;&amp;f\0&amp;&amp;0&amp;&amp;1 \end{bmatrix}$$We use The Matrix T for Affine Transformation. now we just have to code. Apply C++ here shall be easy to understand the process mentioned. 1234567891011121314151617181920212223242526272829303132333435363738394041424344454647484950515253545556575859606162636465666768697071727374757677#include &lt;opencv.hpp&gt;#include &lt;iostream&gt;using namespace std;using namespace cv;class Process&#123;public: ///&lt;函数&gt;仿射变换 ///&lt;参数 &quot;I&quot;&gt;输入原始图像 ///&lt;参数 &quot;A0B0C0&quot;&gt;原图仿射变换基准点 ///&lt;参数 &quot;A1B1C1&quot;&gt;仿射变换目标点 ///&lt;结果&gt;返回Mat型仿射变换之后图像 Mat affine(Mat I, Point2d A0, Point2d B0, Point2d C0, Point2d A1, Point2d B1, Point2d C1) &#123; Mat result(I.rows, I.cols, CV_8UC3); double dst_num[9] = &#123; A0.x, B0.x, C0.x, A0.y, B0.y, C0.y, 1, 1, 1 &#125;; double src_num[9] = &#123; A1.x, B1.x, C1.x, A1.y, B1.y, C1.y, 1, 1, 1 &#125;; Mat src_mat(3, 3, CV_64F, src_num); Mat dst_mat(3, 3, CV_64F, dst_num); //affine transformation matrix 仿射变换矩阵 Mat T = src_mat * dst_mat.inv(); for (int i = 0; i &lt; I.cols; i++) &#123; for (int j = 0; j &lt; I.rows; j++) &#123; double P1_num[3] = &#123; i, j, 1 &#125;; Mat P1_mat(3, 1, CV_64F, P1_num); //cout &lt;&lt; P1_mat &lt;&lt; endl; Mat P0_mat = T*P1_mat; //cout &lt;&lt; P0_mat &lt;&lt; endl; if (P0_mat.at&lt;double&gt;(0, 0) &lt; 0) P0_mat.at&lt;double&gt;(0, 0) = 0; if (P0_mat.at&lt;double&gt;(0, 0) &gt; I.cols - 1) P0_mat.at&lt;double&gt;(0, 0) = I.cols - 1; if (P0_mat.at&lt;double&gt;(1, 0) &lt; 0) P0_mat.at&lt;double&gt;(1, 0) = 0; if (P0_mat.at&lt;double&gt;(1, 0) &gt; I.rows - 1) P0_mat.at&lt;double&gt;(1, 0) = I.rows - 1; Point2d P0(P0_mat.at&lt;double&gt;(0, 0), P0_mat.at&lt;double&gt;(1, 0)); result.at&lt;Vec3b&gt;(P0) = I.at&lt;Vec3b&gt;(j, i); &#125; &#125; //标记原图仿射变换基准点 circle(I, A0, 2, Scalar(0, 0, 255)); circle(I, B0, 2, Scalar(0, 0, 255)); circle(I, C0, 2, Scalar(0, 0, 255)); //标记目标图像仿射变换目标点 circle(result, A1, 2, Scalar(0, 0, 255)); circle(result, B1, 2, Scalar(0, 0, 255)); circle(result, C1, 2, Scalar(0, 0, 255)); return result; &#125;&#125;;void main()&#123; Mat I = imread(&quot;..//chicago.jpg&quot;); Process a; Point2d A0(300, 250); Point2d B0(200, 100); Point2d C0(500, 200); Point2d A1(400, 300); Point2d B1(300, 200); Point2d C1(500, 250); Mat result = a.affine(I, A0, B0, C0, A1, B1, C1); imshow(&quot;ori&quot;, I); imshow(&quot;res&quot;, result); waitKey();&#125; We also have different tiny types for graphics,but it’s not that relative to our target——ECC. 1234567891011121314151617181920212223242526272829303132333435363738394041424344454647484950515253545556575859606162636465666768697071727374757677787980818283848586878889/*1、用仿射变换3x+5加密如下明文：data2、用仿射变换7x+10解密如下密文：